title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1986-06-21
lineage: Master PCM; Recording Equipment: Schoeps CMC42 (Spread Omnis, Spaced 3 Feet Apart with 180 degree angle of incidence) -> Grace 18v Mic Preamp -> MOD PCM-F1; Recording Location: Official Tapers Section; Editing and Mastering: Jamie Waddell on the GEMS Edit Station. Primarily this was emphasis and DC offset removal Weiss Saracon for 16 BIT – 44.1kHz SRC and POWR-3 Dither Tracked in Wavelab, FLAC’d Flac Frontend level 8 - mixing by Kevin Tobin
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, Friend Of The Devil, CC Rider, Loser, Desolation Row, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Saint Of Circumstance-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> He's Gone*-> Smokestack Lightning-> Drums-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E:Not Fade Away-> E: Brokedown Palace

*Dedicated to Len Bias
